			<div class="message">
				<p>
					It sucks. It really sucks. School sucks. There's too much homework and I am clueless as
					to how to do half of it. I'll often ask class mates for an easy way out. These are the general questions:
					<ol>
						<li>Is there homework?</li>
						<li>When is it due?</li>
						<li>How long will it take?</li>
						<li><strike> Can I copy yours?</strike></li>
						<li>What do I have to do?</li>
						<li>How do I do that?</li>
						<li>What workbook?</li>
						<li>What does that mean?</li>
						<li>Please, specifically, how do I actually complete this task?</li>
						<li>Hello?</li>
					</ol>
					<br>
					If I dont get a response, or my friends are equally clueless, I'm stuffed.
				</p>
