			<div class="message">
				<p>
					Right? Right! Someone in my class knows exactly what's going on <em>and</em> wasn't half asleep in that lesson.
					But who? Who do I ask? If only there was a convenient way to message a large group of people and have a
					group discussion, benefiting everone that chooses to take part...
					<h3>Discord!</h3>
					Discord can gather people from all over into one group chat. (Literally, a discord "server" can include several
					thousands of users.) Not only that, but it supports automation - robot users. So we're all set, I made a bot
					that can automatically invite you into the server and put you into group text and voice chats with all your classmates,
					all interfaced through this website!
				</p>
				<p>
					Ever struggling with English? Message your entire English class. Just get discord, (it's easy to sign up) and ask for
